{
  "id": "adv_main_01_13_05",
  "title": "星見編3章15話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sun-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "こんにちは\n少し時間があったので、見学に来ました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello.\nI had some free time‚ so I came to watch.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（それだけを言うと、天動瑠依は黙って）\n（じっとステージ上のさくらを見つめた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Rui Tendo says nothing more)\n(and stares hard at Sakura on stage.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.3666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "…………\n長瀬麻奈さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…\nMana Nagase…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.266666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.1333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "長瀬麻奈さんの再来って言われてますよね\n彼女……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "People are saying she’s Mana Nagase’s second coming‚ right?\nSakura‚ I mean.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.366666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "…………どう思います？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.848910594332047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 20.3
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.31557726099868
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "長瀬麻奈さんの、マネージャーをしていたんですよね\n長瀬麻奈さんの生の歌声を聞き、ステージも見ていた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were Mana Nagase’s manager‚ weren’t you?\nYou heard her singing in person‚ and you watched her perform‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.38224392766538,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.254057987876596
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "その、あなたから見て\nどう思いますか？　さくらさんは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From your vantage point‚\nwhat do you think about Sakura?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.333333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.30985713304526
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてそんなことを？\nDayDreamの子達に聞かれたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you asking me this?\nDid the other DayDream girls ask you about it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.37652379971196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.409857133045264
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "いえ……。彼女達は関係ないです\nただ、私が興味があって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No. They have nothing to do with this.\nI just have a personal interest in it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.40985713304529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.87652379971196
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "長瀬麻奈というアイドルは\nそんなに凄いのかって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was just wondering‚ was Mana Nagase\nreally that amazing as an idol?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.976523799711956,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.70985713304529
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "実は私、長瀬麻奈さんのステージをじかに見たこと\nないんです。映像では何度も見ましたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To be honest‚ I’ve never actually seen Mana Nagase perform live.\nThough I did see videos of her many times.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.476523799711956,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.076523799711964
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……見た限り、そんなに凄くはない\nそういう口振りですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And from what you’ve seen‚ you weren’t that impressed.\nThat’s what it sounds like you’re saying.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.47652379971196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.87652379971197
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "…………正直、そう思いました\n自分の方が勝っているんじゃないかって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To be honest‚ yes‚ that’s how I felt.\nI always thought I was better than her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.77652379971197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "パフォーマンス、歌唱力\nどれも引けを取ってないんじゃないか……でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At performing‚ singing‚\nI thought I had an advantage over her in every category. But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.8098571330453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.64319046637864
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "みんな言うんです……\n長瀬麻奈は凄かったって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone keeps saying it.\nThey keep saying Mana Nagase was amazing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.3098571330453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.30473562040521
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（少し苛立っているのか……）\n（納得がいかないみたいだな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(She sounds a little annoyed…)\n(…as if she’s having a hard time accepting it.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.57140228707189
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "亡くなってしまったので、もう二度と見ることが\n出来ないという想いが、彼女をカリスマにしている",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since she’s passed away‚ no one will ever get\nto hear her sing again—that’s what gives her charisma.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.67140228707188,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.63806895373853
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "……そう思ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s the conclusion I’d reached.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.63806895373853,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……今は違うと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But now you feel differently?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.50473562040526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.63806895373853
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "…………朝倉恭一……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kyoichi Asakura…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.63806895373853,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.93806895373856
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（朝倉恭一。リズノワやトリエルを擁する）\n（バンプロダクションの社長だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Kyoichi Asakura. The owner of groups like LizNoir and TRINITYAiLE‚)\n(and the president of Van Productions.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.83806895373857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.03806895373857
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "私のステージを見て言うんです。全然ダメだって\n長瀬麻奈の足元にも及ばないって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whenever he watches me perform‚ he always tells me I’m no good.\nThat I’m not even close to following in Mana Nagase’s footsteps.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.00473562040526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.87781262662301
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_05-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（ファンや後輩が、強い想いから神格化するのは分かる）\n（けど、朝倉さんなら客観的に見ていたはずだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I can understand how the intense feelings of fans or juniors can deify a person.)\n(But Mr. Asakura must’ve seen everything objectively.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.91114595995637,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.14447929328969
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
